    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "You probably all know from your own experiences the peculiar amnesia, that is, loss of memory, concerning childhood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "I mean the fact that the first years, to the fifth, sixth or eighth, have not left the same traces in our memory as have later experiences.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "The child is able to speak well at the age of two, it soon shows that it can become adjusted to the most complicated psychic situations, and makes remarks which years later are retold to it, but which it has itself entirely forgotten.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Our memory deals selectively with its later materials, with impressions which come to us in later life.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000006_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000006_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "For this reason I have called these childhood memories \"disguise memories,\" memories used to conceal; by means of careful analysis one is able to develop out of them everything that is forgotten.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Beautiful examples of this occur in literature, and I myself can present such an example.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000007_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000007_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "He was a one eyed man, short in stature, stout, his head deeply sunk into his neck.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000007_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000007_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "I concluded from the content that he was a physician.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "After we have interpreted such a dream for the dreamer and he, in the most favorable circumstances does not attack the interpretation itself, he almost always asks the question whence such a wish comes, since it seems foreign to him and he feels conscious of just the opposite sensations. We need not hesitate to point out this origin.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "These evil wish impulses have their origin in the past, often in a past which is not too far away.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "You will wish to conclude therefrom that such wishes and such dreams cannot occur if such changes in the relationship to a person have not taken place; if such relationship was always of the same character.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "You say: \"Granted this death wish was present at some time or other, and is substantiated by memory, yet this is no explanation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "It is long outlived, to day it can be present only in the unconscious and as an empty, emotionless memory, but not as a strong impulse.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Why should it be recalled by the dream at all!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000010_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000010_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "This question is justified.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000010_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000010_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "But I must remain within the bounds of our discussion and practice restraint. Prepare yourselves for the temporary abstention.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000010_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000010_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Let us be satisfied with the circumstantial proof that this outlived wish can be shown to act as a dream stimulator and let us continue the investigation to see whether or not other evil wishes admit of the same derivation out of the past.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "As often as someone has been in our way in life-and how often must this happen in the complicated relationships of life-the dream is ready to do away with him, be he father, mother, brother, sister, spouse, etc",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000011_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000011_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "For the child loves itself first, and later learns to love others, to sacrifice something of its ego for another.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000012_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000012_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Expressions such as \"I don't want him!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000012_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000012_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Let the stork take him away again,\" are very usual.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000012_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000012_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Subsequently every opportunity is made use of to disparage the new arrival, and even attempts to do him bodily harm, direct attacks, are not unheard of.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000012_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000012_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "If the difference in age is greater, the new child may awaken certain sympathies as an interesting object, as a sort of living doll, and if the difference is eight years or more, motherly impulses, especially in the case of girls, may come into play.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "I believe it was Bernard Shaw who said: \"If there is anyone who hates a young English lady more than does her mother, it is her elder sister.\" There is something about this saying, however, that arouses our antipathy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000013_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000013_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "We can, at a pinch, understand hatred of brothers and sisters, and rivalry among them, but how may feelings of hatred force their way into the relationship between daughter and mother, parents and children?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "This relationship is without doubt the more favorable, even when looked at from the viewpoint of the child.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "This is in accord with our expectation; we find it much more offensive for love between parents and children to be lacking than for love between brothers and sisters.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000014_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000014_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "The motives for this are everywhere known and disclose a tendency to separate those of the same sex, daughter from mother, father from son.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000014_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000014_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Impatient waiting for the death of the father grows to heights approximating tragedy in the case of a successor to the throne.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000014_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000014_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Less strained is the relationship between father and daughter, mother and son.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Because there is an unmistakable disposition to deny their significance in life, and to set forth the ideal demanded by society as a fulfilled thing much oftener than it really is fulfilled.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "But it is preferable for psychology to speak the truth, rather than that this task should be left to the cynic.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8975_270782_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8975/270782/8975_270782_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "It is not to be wondered at that in the case of a large number of people the dream discloses the wish for the removal of the parents, especially the parent of the same sex.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
