        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "The reason for this is that the deepest and most uniform motive for becoming unfriendly, especially between persons of the same sex, has already made its influence felt in earliest childhood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
