        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "Just think of the scandalized opinion of the fine old lady about her uninterpreted dream of \"services of love.\" The problem is not yet solved, and it is still possible that upon further study of the evil in the dream we shall come to some other decision and arrive at another valuation of human nature.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
