        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "As a result of the whole investigation we grasp two facts, which, however, disclose only the beginnings of new riddles, new doubts.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
