        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "It not only translates our thoughts into a primitive form of expression, but it reawakens the peculiarities of our primitive psychic life, the ancient predominance of the ego, the earliest impulses of our sexual life, even our old intellectual property, if we may consider the symbolic relations as such.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
