        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8975",
        "content": "The time will soon come, however, when we shall clothe the unconscious character of the latent dream thought with another name, which shall differentiate it from the unconscious out of the realm of the infantile.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
